# Application layer

Путь: `app/Application/{BC}/{Command|Query|DTO|Presenter|ReadPort}`.

Naming: English only. No Russian. No transliteration.

## Allowed

- Command / Query + handlers for **this** BC only
- DTO, Presenter interfaces, ReadPort interfaces
- Use `App\Domain\{same BC}\...` and `App\Shared\...` / `App\Application\Shared\...`
- Publish pulled domain events via `DomainEventPublisher`

## Forbidden

- Import another BC’s `Command\*Handler`, `Query\*Handler`, Application services
- Call another BC’s use case / handler / ReadPort / repository from a handler
- Put SQL, Eloquent, HTTP, controllers here
- Bypass domain invariants (no anemic “setters” around aggregates)

## Cross-BC mutations

Handlers of BC A must **not** invoke handlers of BC B.  
Integration is **event-driven only**: after save, publish domain events; other BC’s policies/listeners react and run **their own** commands.

```php
// ❌ BAD — Order handler opens Workshop use case directly
$this->openProductionTaskHandler->handle(new OpenProductionTaskCommand(...));

// ✅ GOOD — Order publishes events; Workshop listener reacts
$this->orders->save($order);
$this->events->publish($order->pullDomainEvents());
```

Read-side: a Query may use only **own** `ReadPort`. No cross-BC read ports inside a handler (compose at Interface/Infrastructure if needed).

## Structure

| Folder | Role |
|--------|------|
| `Command` | Write use cases + handlers |
| `Query` | Read use cases + handlers |
| `DTO` | Transport shapes |
| `ReadPort` | Read model ports (interfaces) |
| `Presenter` | Output shaping ports (interfaces) |
